---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Home"
  desc="The portfolio, blog and chronicles of misadventures for Frank Stallone III"
>
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <div class="center">
      <article class="hero">
        <Header />
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display-alt">
            üëãüèº Hiya! I love <span class="font-variants-01">TECHNOLOGY</span>,
            MINDFULNESS, and CRE<span class="font-variants-02"
              ><span class="font-variants-01-ls">A</span></span
            ><span class="font-variants-01">T</span>ING compelling user
            experiences.
          </h2>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
  <main class="wrapper" role="main" id="main-content">
    <article class="region flow">
      <h2>Featured work</h2>
      <hgroup>
        <h3 class="uppercase">
          <span class="font-variants-01">R</span>oll
        </h3>
        <h4>UX, UI, Design system</h4>
      </hgroup>
      <p>
        Created a new way to run payroll, and manage small business owner's <abbr
          title="Human Capital Management">HCM</abbr
        > needs on the go, with a mobile first approach. From concept to customer.
      </p>
      <article class="grid">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/roll-squared-01@2x.png"
          alt="Mock up of the original logo design for Roll by ADP"
        />
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/roll-squared-02@2x.png"
          alt="Screenshot of VSCode showing the design tokens repository for Roll by ADP"
        />
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/roll-squared-03@2x.png"
          alt="Screenshot of the payroll run conversation UI showcasing the components design and created for our clients"
        />
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/roll-squared-04@2x.png"
          alt="Screenshots of the mobile app that would eventually be used circa 2018"
        />
      </article>
    </article>
    <article class="region flow">
      <hgroup>
        <h3
          class="px-4 pt-4 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-display text-amber-amber12 hover:underline uppercase"
        >
          Builde<span class="font-variants-01">r</span>s <span
            class="font-variants-01 tracking-flat">T</span
          >rus<span class="font-variants-02">t</span> Capital
        </h3>
        <h4
          class="px-4 pb-4 text-xl xl:text-2xl font-display text-amber-amber11 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3"
        >
          Brand transformation
        </h4>
      </hgroup>
      <p class="px-4 pb-8 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 font-bold">
        Created a sophisticated brand that appealed to their entrepreneur
        clientele, and resonated with their core values of trust, stability, and
        transparency.
      </p>
      <article
        class="grid gap-4 px-4 place-items-center xs:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 md:grid-rows-2 lg:grid-cols-8 lg:grid-rows-8 pb-4"
      >
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/btc-squared-01@2x.png"
          alt="Photo of initial sketches of the chosen logo for Builders Trust Capital showing the intentions for the three pilars"
        />
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/btc-squared-02@2x.png"
          alt="Screenshot of the home page design for Builders Trust Capital"
        />
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/btc-squared-03@2x.png"
          alt="Screenshot of the presentation for the new Builders Trust Capital logo in context on a sign and business cards"
        /><img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/btc-squared-04@2x.png"
          alt="Logo presentation of the Builders Trust Capital mark and logo type"
        />
      </article>
    </article>
    <h2 class="sr-only">Other logo and branding work</h2>
    <article class="region flow">
      <hegroup>
        <h3
          class="px-4 pt-4 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-display text-amber-amber12 hover:underline uppercase"
        >
          NJC Stone Supply
        </h3>
        <h4
          class="px-4 pb-4 text-xl xl:text-2xl font-display text-amber-amber11"
        >
          Logo
        </h4>
      </hegroup>
      <p class="px-4 pb-8 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 font-bold">
        Designed a logo mark, and logo type that speaks equally to Noah's
        audience as it does Noah's work.
      </p>
      <article
        class="grid gap-4 px-4 place-items-center xs:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 pb-4"
      >
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/njc-squared-01@2x.png"
          alt="The logo mark for Noah James Curtis Stone Supply & Tree Service"
        />
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/njc-squared-02@2x.png"
          alt="The typeface and colors chosen for the branding of Noah James Curtis Stone Supply & Tree Service"
        />
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/njc-squared-03@2x.png"
          alt="Screenshot of the grid used for one of the Noah James Curtis Stone Supply logos with type"
        />
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/njc-squared-04@2x.png"
          alt="One of the variations of the NJC Stone Supply & Tree Service with logo mark and type logo"
        />
      </article>
    </article>
    <article class="region flow">
      <hgroup>
        <h3
          class="px-4 pt-4 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-display text-amber-amber12 uppercase"
        >
          Bracke<span class="font-variants-02">t</span>s Podcast
        </h3>
        <h4
          class="px-4 pb-4 text-xl xl:text-2xl font-display text-amber-amber11"
        >
          Co-host, Logo, Branding
        </h4>
      </hgroup>
      <p class="px-4 pb-8 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 font-bold">
        Co-create a technology podcast that serves as the pulse of tech within
        ADP.
      </p>
      <article
        class="grid gap-4 px-4 place-items-center xs:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 pb-4"
      >
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/brackets-squared-01@2x.png"
          alt="The original logo mark and type logo for ADP's Developer Community Brackets Podcast"
        />
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/brackets-squared-02@2x.png"
          alt="The original logo mark for ADP's Developer Community Brackets Podcast"
        />
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/brackets-squared-03@2x.png"
          alt="Play on the ADP's Developer Community Brackets Podcast logo"
        />
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/brackets-squared-04@2x.png"
          alt="Another spin of the design of the ADP's Developer Community Brackets Podcast logo"
        />
      </article>
    </article>
    <article class="region flow">
      <hgroup>
        <h3
          class="px-4 pt-4 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-display text-amber-amber12 uppercase"
        >
          S<span class="font-variants-02">a</span><span
            class="font-variants-02 -ml-3">v</span
          >ani
        </h3>
        <h4
          class="px-4 pb-4 text-xl xl:text-2xl font-display text-amber-amber11"
        >
          Logo, Branding
        </h4>
      </hgroup>
      <p class="px-4 pb-8 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 font-bold">
        Brought a niche Volkswagen parts company closer to it's audience with
        new branding.
      </p>
      <article
        class="grid gap-4 px-4 place-items-center xs:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 pb-4"
      >
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="/assets/squared/savani-squared-01@2x.png"
          alt="The original logo mark for Savani Auto Parts"
        />
        <a
          href="/assets/btc/builders-trust-capital-design-system-3.1.pdf"
          class="xs:square"
          ><img
            loading="lazy"
            src="/assets/squared/savani-squared-02@2x.png"
            alt="The type logo for Savani Auto Parts"
          /></a
        >
        <a
          href="/assets/roll/roll-ui-kit-foundiation--design-system-2021.pdf"
          class="xs:square"
          ><img
            loading="lazy"
            src="/assets/squared/savani-squared-03@2x.png"
            alt="The logo mark and type logo for Savani Auto Parts"
          /></a
        >
        <a
          href="/assets/prezzp/prezzo.it-design-system-2.1.pdf"
          class="xs:square"
          ><img
            loading="lazy"
            src="/assets/squared/savani-squared-04@2x.png"
            alt="A t-shirt with the Savani Auto Parts logo mark and type logo"
          /></a
        >
      </article>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
